Program: Outlook
Title: 12/07/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00v3y0w
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 13 Jul 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, Jo Fidgen meets a Greek Orthodox priest who tells us how the economic crisis has affected his parishioners and challenged his faith. A top French perfumer on the pros and cons of having an exceptional sense of smell; and the Delhi rapper who is using hip hop, art and dance to change the lives of disadvantaged children in the city. Show less